episodes.title: Members of cultlike group tied to murders held without bail
episodes.description:
Jack Lasota, 34 and Michelle Zajko, 33, who were arrested in Maryland after police say they were tied to a group called the Zizians which is linked to multiple homicides, have been held without bail.
